items.text:
In your time together, Quisi has made a game of scouring Lone Tree
Station for clues as to the kitchen’s whereabouts. Eventually, the scent
of Hy Pimpot’s biscuits grows stronger, and Quisi cheers. “Yes! Yes!
Yes! Delicious biscuits, here I come!” She runs off.
Each Ranger soothes 2 fatigue, then discard Quisi.
